sellerCard.description: Enterprise web developer experienced in web design and development, data modeling, cross-browser user interface design and programming, translating business requirements to technical specifications, experience of creating logical and innovative solutions to complex problems.

description.content:
.I have been developing websites in the Laravel framework since 2018. I have worked on multiple Laravel websites. I will provide the services to develop the web application in the Laravel framework according to the client's requirements. I will also fix the bugs in the developed website.


With this gig, I can


Develop the complete website in the Laravel framework.

  • Fix Laravel issues and problems.
  • Create REST APIS for mobile applications.
  • Database Integration.
  • Payment Gateway Integration.
  • Fix HTML and CSS issues.
  • Add custom jQuery plugins.



Note: Please contact me before placing an order so that there will be no issue for you and me and that everything will be clear before starting the work. Please also contact/message me before requesting any revision, In revisions, only minor changes are allowed no new functionality is allowed in revisions.

packageList.title: Basic Package
packageList.description: i will fix the issues of your website developed in Laravel framework.

packageList.title: Standard Package
packageList.description: In this package I develop the websites that contains up to 5 pages with some extra features.

packageList.title: Premium Package
packageList.description: In this package I will provide some advance features like eCommerce, payment methods, etc.
